Package: thunderbolt-tbfix-dkms
Version: @VERSION@
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms (>= 2.1.0.0), kmod, make, libc6
Maintainer: AppMana <ops@appmana.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/AppMana/thunderbolt-tbfix
Description: AppMana Thunderbolt and Thunderbolt-net kernel module fixes
 DKMS source package for AppMana's patched thunderbolt.ko and
 thunderbolt_net.ko modules. This package installs source under /usr/src and
 registers it with DKMS so the modules are rebuilt for the running kernel and
 future kernel upgrades.
